---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden section-surface" style="border-top: 1px solid #221A2C;">
  <!-- Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cyber-void opacity-30" />

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-6 items-center">
      <!-- Text — left -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="section-label">
          Philosophy
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight" style="color: #E4DDE8;">
          Own Your Digital Space
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #9A8FA8;">
          <p>
            The Wired is built on <strong style="color: #889880; font-weight: 600;">Nostr</strong> — an open,
            censorship-resistant protocol. Your identity is a cryptographic key pair that you control.
            No email signups, no phone numbers, no central authority.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your content lives across a network of relays, not locked inside
            a single company's servers. Switch apps, switch relays — your data
            follows you because <strong style="color: #E4DDE8; font-weight: 600;">you own it</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe social media should serve its users, not exploit them.
            No ads, no algorithms manipulating your feed, no data harvesting.
            Just your community, your way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Character — center -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex items-end justify-center relative">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[250px] h-[250px] rounded-full blur-[80px]"
          style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #60706030, #78587020, transparent);"
        />
        <img
          src="/characters/cyber-girl.png"
          alt=""
          class="relative w-[240px] h-auto"
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px #60706038) drop-shadow(0 0 60px #78587028) drop-shadow(0 0 100px #60706018);"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Principle cards — right -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3 hover-lift group"
          style="background: #221A2C; border: 0.5px solid #2E2440;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            style="background: #1E1824;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: #785870;">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
              <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="2" />
              <circle cx="20" cy="6" r="2" />
              <circle cx="4" cy="18" r="2" />
              <circle cx="20" cy="18" r="2" />
              <line x1="6" y1="6.5" x2="9.5" y2="10" />
              <line x1="18" y1="6.5" x2="14.5" y2="10" />
              <line x1="6" y1="17.5" x2="9.5" y2="14" />
              <line x1="18" y1="17.5" x2="14.5" y2="14" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-base" style="color: #E4DDE8;">Decentralized</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #9A8FA8;">
            No single point of failure. Your content is distributed across relays you choose.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3 hover-lift group"
          style="background: #221A2C; border: 0.5px solid #2E2440;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            style="background: #1E1824;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: #785870;">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" />
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-base" style="color: #E4DDE8;">Encrypted</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #9A8FA8;">
            Cryptographic key pairs for identity. Private messages with end-to-end encryption.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3 hover-lift group"
          style="background: #221A2C; border: 0.5px solid #2E2440;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            style="background: #1E1824;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: #785870;">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
              <polyline points="9,12 11,14 15,10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-base" style="color: #E4DDE8;">Sovereign</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #9A8FA8;">
            You own your keys, your data, your identity. No account can be banned or deleted.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3 hover-lift group"
          style="background: #221A2C; border: 0.5px solid #2E2440;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            style="background: #1E1824;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: #785870;">
              <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6" />
              <polyline points="15,3 21,3 21,9" />
              <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-base" style="color: #E4DDE8;">Open Source</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #9A8FA8;">
            Fully open source. Inspect the code, contribute, or fork it. Transparency by design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
